{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "红娘子揭露赤练蛇在毒药中浸泡数十年的秘密，暗示其与大蜈蚣关系密切。王动趁机挑拨赤练蛇与催命符、红娘子之间的关系，以\"分馒头\"为喻，劝说赤练蛇与自己结盟对付崔老大。赤练蛇逐渐动摇。三人回到屋内，催命符搜查后只剩两个稻草人。催命符察觉稻草人异常臃肿，突然出手双飞游魂刺刺入稻草人心脏，王动脸色骤变——稻草人内藏的正是他与燕七约定的最后一击。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我一向总觉得最了解我的人就是你，你知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为只有女人才能了解女人，这道理谁都知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "他是女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你以为他是男人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "看起来他好像是男的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "就算他本来是个男人，但在毒药里泡了几十年，也早就变成个女人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "这是他最大的秘密，我本来不该说出来的，幸好你也不是外人，所以……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我还可以告诉你个秘密。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "什么秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红娘子",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我知道他和大蜈蚣是好朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_hong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你错了，他们不是朋友，他们已是……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "她说的话，我本来连一个字都不信的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你本来不笨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "可是她说的若不是真的，你何必要她的命？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你是不是也想叫我要你的命？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我这条命早已不姓王了，谁要去都没关系，但你呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "我怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "没有人伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "有没有人开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "你也知道她恨你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "她为什么一直没有要你的命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为她知道我活着比死了有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "以后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "以后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "以后分钱的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "大蜈蚣死了，他们是不是也很伤心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "他们为什么不伤心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "因为三个人分钱，总比四个人分得多些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "若只有两个人分钱呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你究竟想说什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我想说的事，你本该早就明白了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "一个馒头两人吃，总比三个人吃好些，这道理本就谁都明白，现在的问题是，是哪两个人能吃到馒头呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我知道你的功夫，你当然不怕红娘子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "但她和崔老大是什么关系？你和崔老大又是什么关系？你能不能比得上她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "所以你若想吃到馒头，就最好赶快另想法子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "另外找个人，来帮你抢那馒头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "找什么人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "第一，那人要不太贪心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "世上有这种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我就不是贪心的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "以前我也许不是，但现在我已懂得，两个人分馒头吃，总比没有馒头吃好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "第二呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "第二，那人要不如你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么要不如我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "因为他若不如你，就绝不敢在你面前动歪脑筋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你不如我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我若比你强，现在怎会要你背着我呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你真是站在我这边的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我只有站在你这边。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "因为他们那边的人已太挤了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你能够替我做些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "我还有手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你的手能做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "至少还能拉住一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "现在只有一个问题了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "你能不能对付崔老大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_wang_dong",
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "text": "若真的动手，我不知道，但若骤出不意，攻其无备，那就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_lian_she",
      "speaker_name": "赤练蛇",
      "listener": "char_cui_ming_fu",
      "text": "你们已看过了。",
